      <h3>How to use this App</h3>
      <p>With all appropriate particle hooks setup, once you press the start button your device will be sent back a ride id. This is then used to publish to every couple of seconds. The server then takes these publishes and sends the current cadence back to the device along with logging it on the server. Statistics about each ride can be viewed from the <a href="/cadence">cadence page</a>.</p>
